OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,6,Ffine, although windy and rather cloudy
OL,7,Ffor a time midweek. Temperatures near
OL,8,Fnormal overall, but tempered by the
OL,9,Fwind at first, with some chilly starts
OL,10,Fstill likely later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
